ing: 1 (14.5 ounce) can diced tomatoes with green chile peppers
2 (10.75 ounce) cans  condensed cream of chicken soup
des: "Try this zippy new dip with tortilla chips! Packed with chicken flavor and mildly spicy, it's sure to be a hit!"
ins: In a medium saucepan over medium heat, mix together the chicken, diced tomatoes with green chile peppers, cream cheese and cream of chicken soup. Cook 20 minutes, stirring frequently, until the dip begins to thicken.
